# Testing Record

## Project: Cyber Shield – Spot the Phishing Scam

### Project Type: Educational Browser Game (HTML, CSS, JavaScript)

---

# Testing Objectives

The testing process was conducted to ensure:

* gameplay functions correctly
* phishing scenarios are understandable for ages 10–12
* accessibility requirements are met
* mobile responsiveness works properly
* educational objectives are achieved
* bugs are identified and resolved

