# Educational Testing Summary

The phishing scenarios were tested to ensure:

* language matched ages 10–12
* questions were easy to understand
* explanations supported learning
* scenarios reflected realistic phishing examples
* educational outcomes were clear

---

# Testing Reflection

Testing helped identify issues related to responsiveness, scoring logic, accessibility, and content readability. Iterative testing improved gameplay quality and ensured the game remained suitable for younger audiences while maintaining educational effectiveness.
